{"tid":1189990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撐69，反惡法，反5毛用任何命題分化模糊焦點","createTime":"2019-06-07T05:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T08:46:06.000Z","uid":12149,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d9f035e8da5be64490f5b52d974cfbedcff4dbfc","tid":1189990,"uid":12149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:44:38.000Z","msg":"大家69出黎遊行係為自己，為香港，為未來。唔係為左支持邊個既立場而出。你自己有自由意志，可以選擇任何方式<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">反對修例</span>，選擇你認為合適既方式就得。<br />\n<br />\n至於咩黑衫白衫，表唔表態，<span style=\"color: red;\">甚至今日既汽油彈</span>，可能聽日以至69之後日日都有新topic 。你淨係記住你係<span style=\"color: red;\">反對修例就夠</span>。<br />\n<br />\n3毛/5毛依家好鍾意係咁利用話題製造2元對立同分化人心引發各種討論淡化69<br />\n<br />\n舉汽油彈為例：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">咩動機邊個做係唔係鬼重要咩？？你係反對修例就係反對架啦，佢如果真係義士做既你咪默默支持，如果係鬼想破壞香港人團結就更加唔應該動搖啦，總之你都係反修例架啦。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>結論，撐69，反修例先係個重點</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"8e636965dde38b6230c11630b5ebdd47f2bd8731","tid":1189990,"uid":12149,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:50:18.000Z","msg":"Push黑色5毛警報"},{"pid":"e3f6db943b56d1442dded8a394812f68af764329","tid":1189990,"uid":12149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dddac69f21e7966652ad338c9ac864a0d5f31f22","tid":1189990,"uid":12149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ccf1b1e6556df82cf463def67653fce488df99","tid":1189990,"uid":12149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T05:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr